{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{}},"slideshow_FtMhKD":{"type":"slideshow","blocks":{"hero_7yRcWC":{"type":"hero","settings":{"top_subheading":"","title":"","title_size":80,"subheading":"","link":"","link_text":"","link_2":"","link_text_2":"","button_color_scheme":"","text_align":"vertical-bottom horizontal-left","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Copy_of_Untitled-3.jpg","overlay_opacity":0}}},"block_order":["hero_7yRcWC"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"full_width":true,"desktop_size":0,"mobile_size":0,"style":"arrows","autoplay":true,"autoplay_speed":7}},"advanced_content_prGQN9":{"type":"advanced-content","blocks":{"liquid_UqznJB":{"type":"liquid","settings":{"code":"<center><h1>Explore Fyxx Shop & Liquor Store<\/h1><\/center>","width":"100%","alignment":"center"}},"liquid_7a3ygU":{"type":"liquid","settings":{"code":"<center><h1>Explore Fyxx Shop & Liquor Store<\/h1><\/center>","width":"100%","alignment":"center"}}},"block_order":["liquid_UqznJB","liquid_7a3ygU"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"full_width":false,"space_around":true}},"rich_text_6wBtm6":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_yYpyGF":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Explore Fyxx Shop & Liquor Store","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_7hQw6a":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":true,"text":"<p>Fyxx Shop was born from a desire to create more than just a retail store. We envisioned a space where people could enjoy a glass of wine or a hand-crafted cocktail, but also a place to connect—whether it’s a quick stop during your day or a leisurely evening.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_yYpyGF","text_7hQw6a"],"settings":{"align_text":"center","narrow_column":true,"color_scheme":"none","divider":false}},"background_image_text_w8nqej":{"type":"background-image-text","settings":{"subtitle":"","title":"The Shop","text":"<p>We created a shop that is open, friendly, and interactive, reflecting both our ethos and our carefully curated wines, spirits and cigar collection. Over time, our vision has matured, transforming Fyxx into a destination that inspires.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC02149.jpg","layout":"right","height":550,"parallax":true,"parallax_direction":"left"}},"text_and_image_XeXBCU":{"type":"text-and-image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-15_at_17.25.38.jpg","image_mask":"portrait","image2":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Buy_Pay_Online_-_Sunset_Ads_1080_x_1920_px.jpg","image2_mask":"portrait","subtitle":"","title":"Fyxx Cigar Room","heading_size":"h2","text":"<p>We offer a selection of genuine, premium cigars, stored in a humidity-controlled room. Our range includes both Old World classics and New World favorites.<\/p>","button_label":"Browse Cigar Collection","button_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/cigars","button_style":"secondary","align_text":"left","image_width":"66","layout":"right","color_scheme":"none","divider":false,"top_padding":true,"bottom_padding":true}},"text_and_image_KxiP7g":{"type":"text-and-image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC02142.jpg","image_mask":"none","image2":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC00006.jpg","image2_mask":"none","subtitle":"","title":"Fyxx Spirits","heading_size":"h2","text":"<p>Our shelves feature a range of premium spirits—from single malts and small-batch gins to artisanal mezcals, tequilas, vodkas, and beyond—handpicked for quality, character, and craft.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_style":"primary","align_text":"left","image_width":"66","layout":"left","color_scheme":"none","divider":false,"top_padding":true,"bottom_padding":true}},"text_and_image_87DNbz":{"type":"text-and-image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Untitled_design-26.png","image_mask":"none","image2":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC00817.jpg","image2_mask":"none","subtitle":"","title":"Fyxx Chilled Room","heading_size":"h2","text":"<p>Through the glass door, you’ll find a curated selection of wines stored at the optimal temperature. Step inside, take your time, and find something special.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_style":"primary","align_text":"left","image_width":"66","layout":"right","color_scheme":"none","divider":false,"top_padding":true,"bottom_padding":true}},"text_and_image_M4J4bi":{"type":"text-and-image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC05308.jpg","image_mask":"square","image2":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/WhatsApp_Image_2021-09-10_at_1.19.44_PM_3.jpg","image2_mask":"square","subtitle":"","title":"Wine On Tap","heading_size":"h2","text":"<p>Our self-serve wine dispenser lets you taste by the glass, with each pour preserved using argon gas to stay fresh. Selections rotate weekly—just load your Fyxx card, choose your pour, and explore at your own pace.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_style":"primary","align_text":"left","image_width":"66","layout":"left","color_scheme":"none","divider":false,"top_padding":true,"bottom_padding":true}},"text_and_image_UCNT7w":{"type":"text-and-image","custom_css":[],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-15_at_18.16.59.jpg","image_mask":"none","image2":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC06631.jpg","image2_mask":"none","subtitle":"","title":"The Green Room","heading_size":"h2","text":"<p>Tucked behind a hidden door, up the staircase, The Green Room is an intimate space built around music, food, and drinks. It’s a place to connect, explore new flavors, and experience something different.<\/p><p><a href=\"\/pages\/the-green-room\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"The Green Room\"><strong>Learn More<\/strong><\/a><\/p>","button_label":"Book a Table","button_link":"https:\/\/widget.servmeco.com\/?oid=1652&source=venue_website","button_style":"primary","align_text":"left","image_width":"66","layout":"right","color_scheme":"3","divider":false,"top_padding":true,"bottom_padding":true}}},"order":["main","slideshow_FtMhKD","advanced_content_prGQN9","rich_text_6wBtm6","background_image_text_w8nqej","text_and_image_XeXBCU","text_and_image_KxiP7g","text_and_image_87DNbz","text_and_image_M4J4bi","text_and_image_UCNT7w"]}